author: Josh Dawsey
title: New York City Mayor Bill de Blasio Makes a Trip to Israel
text:
New York City Mayor Bill de Blasio’s three-day visit to Israel this weekend comes amid a renewed period of unrest in the region.
In a sign of the politics surrounding the trip—a time-honored tradition for New York City mayors—Mr. de Blasio planned to visit victims of terrorist attacks in Israel but also Palestinian children.
